AppSettings
===========

AppSettings is an ActiveRecord plugin for storing application settings in the application database.
It provides the AppSettingsData ActiveRecord class, which loads all settings data on server startup. 
This class provides a convenient way to load application settings as constants under it, for example:
AppSettingsData::MAXIMUM_ALLOWANCE = 7

